desc: Tide yourself over. When sea-salty cravings strike, save your taste buds and our oceans with a good-for-you, good-for-the planet snack. These puffed kelp chips pack an umami kick and satisfying crunch while nourishing your body and restoring our oceans.

layout.text: When you pop open a bag of our kelp chips, you're diving headlong into a savory, healthy way to make a big impact on our oceans.
